lead_paragraph: Jermaine Jones scored in the 47th minute and the Colorado Rapids beat Real Salt Lake 1-0 on Saturday night in the Rocky Mountain Cup.

headline.print_headline: Colorado Holds Top Spot in West With 1-0 Win Over RSL
